short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add a spark of genius to your browser with Jessie Brawl Stars Live Wallpaper, showcasing the beloved gadgeteer in action!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Transform your new tab into a tribute to Jessie, the brilliant inventor from Brawl Stars! With this extension, you’ll enjoy a live wallpaper featuring Jessie and her trusty turret, Scrappy, bringing her tech-savvy energy to every browsing session. It’s the perfect choice for Brawl Stars fans who love her strategic style.

Key Features
🎨 Dynamic Live Wallpaper: Jessie's adventurous spirit animates your Chrome background.
🔍 Google Search Bar: Enjoy seamless web searching integrated into your new tab.
🕒 Clock & Date Display: Stay on schedule with a sleek clock and date feature.
📌 Customizable Shortcuts: Add or remove shortcuts to your favorite websites.
⚙️ Extension Menu: Easily manage or remove the extension with controls in the bottom-left corner.
Let Jessie’s inventive spirit inspire your day as you browse! Whether you’re a tech enthusiast or a fan of Brawl Stars, this live wallpaper brings Jessie’s world to life.
